# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Planning / process artifacts — LOCAL ONLY, never published.
#
# These directories and files are kept on every maintainer's disk but are
# deliberately NOT tracked in git. They are the SDD / spec-writer / superpowers
# scaffolding (specs, designs, plans, discovery notes, the constitution, and the
# AI-assistant guide). They are private working material, not part of the
# shipped product, and must never appear in the published repository.
#
# NOTE: some skills (notably `/sdd:*`) will try to `git add` these. For THIS
# repository that instruction is overridden — see CLAUDE.md. Do not commit them,
# and never `git add --force` them.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.sdd/
discovery/
specs/
docs/superpowers/
CONSTITUTION.md
CLAUDE.md

# Per-user / per-machine plugin state (don't commit; users have their own)
.claude/
.midnight-expert/

# Brainstorming visual-companion scratch (mockups; not part of the project)
.superpowers/

# Node dependencies (regenerable; never commit)
node_modules/
